-spotted-shooting-for-P-K/Article1-1128354.aspx|publisher=Hindustan Times|accessdate=2013-10-16|date=2013-02-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007202357/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/Aamir-Khan-spotted-shooting-for-P-K/Article1-1128354.aspx|archivedate=2013-10-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan shoots for 'PK' in Delhi|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-09-28/news-interviews/42480623_1_aamir-khan-pk-anushka-sharma|publisher=The Times of India|accessdate=2013-09-28|date=2013-10-16|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016083540/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2013-09-28/news-interviews/42480623_1_aamir-khan-pk-anushka-sharma|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Peekay': Aamir Khan amazes fans in Delhi with his new look|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/peekay-aamir-khan-amazes-fans-in-delhi-with-his-new-look/425031-8-66.html|publisher=IBN Live|accessdate=2013-09-28|date=2013-10-16|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007214918/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/peekay-aamir-khan-amazes-fans-in-delhi-with-his-new-look/425031-8-66.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当剧组在德里的[[月光集市|月光集市]]取景时，2013年10月一份第一调查报告指出电影制片人涉嫌伤害宗教感情<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-3542780221.html|title=How Protests against 'PK' Have Unwittingly Validated the Film's Message|publisher=Daily News and Analysis|accessdate=2015-01-31|date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329163829/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-3542780221.html|archive-date=2015-03-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。影片中一名身穿印度[[湿婆神|湿婆神]]装扮的男子，与两名穿[[罩袍|罩袍]]的女性乘坐人力车的场景引来了非议<ref>{{cite web|title= FIR lodged against director, actors of Aamir Khan's 'P.K.'|url= http://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/fir-lodged-against-director-actors-of-aamir-khan-s-p-k/article1-1133798.aspx|date= 2013-10-11|work= Hindustan Times|accessdate= 2013-11-23|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131115090924/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Entertainment/Bollywood/FIR-lodged-against-director-actors-of-Aamir-Khan-s-P-K/Article1-1133798.aspx|archivedate= 2013-11-15}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
影片于2014年12月19日上映，是2014年第200部宝莱坞电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficeindia.com/Details/art_detail/releasecounthits200forfirsttimepk200threleaseof2014 |title=Release Count Hits 200 For First Time – PK 200th Release of 2014 |publisher=Box Office India |date=2015-01-17 |accessdate=2015-06-13 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923225325/http://www.boxofficeindia.com/Details/art_detail/releasecounthits200forfirsttimepk200threleaseof2014 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/PK-is-the-200th-release-of-2014/articleshow/45544870.cms |title=PK is the 200th release of 2014 |work=The Times of India |date=2015-01-17 |accessdate=2015-06-13 |archive-date=2019-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012140902/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/PK-is-the-200th-release-of-2014/articleshow/45544870.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片的上映后来扩展至全球范围内的6000块螢幕，包括844塊海外螢幕<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/box-office/PK-Box-Office-Can-it-be-the-biggest-hit-of-2014/articleshow/45613610.cms|title=PK Box Office: Can it be the biggest hit of 2014?|work=The Times of India|access-date=2015-06-13|archive-date=2022-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220401175255/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/box-office/PK-Box-Office-Can-it-be-the-biggest-hit-of-2014/articleshow/45613610.cms}}</ref>。电影最初在全球4844块螢幕上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/pk-to-reach-4-844-screens-worldwide-tomorrow-114121800482_1.html|title=PK to reach 4,844 screens worldwide tomorrow|author=Urvi Malvania|date=2014-12-20|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206103527/https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/pk-to-reach-4-844-screens-worldwide-tomorrow-114121800482_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan’s ‘PK’ to release in over 6,000 screens in India, overseas – The American Bazaar|url=http://www.americanbazaaronline.com/2014/12/14/aamir-khans-pk-release-6000-screens-india-overseas/|publisher=Americanbazaaronline.com|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2014-12-14|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206233533/https://www.americanbazaaronline.com/2014/12/14/aamir-khans-pk-release-6000-screens-india-overseas/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deccanherald.com/content/449269/aamirs-pk-garners-rs-95.html|title=Aamir's 'PK' garners Rs 95 cr in three days|publisher=Deccan Herald|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2014-12-22|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205005804/https://www.deccanherald.com/content/449269/aamirs-pk-garners-rs-95.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan's PK to be the biggest release in India? : Bollywood, News – India Today|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/aamir-khan-pk-anushka-sharma-sushant-singh-rajput-rajkumar-hirani-sanjay-dutt/1/406946.html|publisher=Indiatoday.intoday.in|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2014-12-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304113314/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/aamir-khan-pk-anushka-sharma-sushant-singh-rajput-rajkumar-hirani-sanjay-dutt/1/406946.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片已获得[[北方邦|北方邦]]和[[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]免税<ref>{{cite web|title=If tax breaks for PK are alright, why not a subsidy for Satanic Verses?|url=http://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/if-tax-breaks-for-pk-are-alright-why-not-a-subsidy-for-satanic-verses-2026655.html|website=Firstpost|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2015-01-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108125421/https://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/if-tax-breaks-for-pk-are-alright-why-not-a-subsidy-for-satanic-verses-2026655.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=PK now made tax-free in Bihar|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/3752517/PK-now-made-tax-free-in-Bihar|publisher=BollywoodHungama.com|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2015-01-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031904/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/news/3752517/PK-now-made-tax-free-in-Bihar|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=After UP, Bihar also declares Aamir Khan’s PK tax-free|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/after-up-bihar-also-declares-aamir-khans-pk-tax-free/|publisher=The Indian Express|accessdate=2015-04-15|date=2015-01-02|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206142343/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/after-up-bihar-also-declares-aamir-khans-pk-tax-free/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影在英国（198块螢幕）、巴基斯坦（超过70块螢幕）、澳大利亚（35块螢幕）和印度海外（超过40个海外市场的844块螢幕）是上映范围最广的印度电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-indias-pk-get-broad-759208|title=Disney India's 'PK' to Get Broad Worldwide Release|author=Nyay Bhushan|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2014-12-18|accessdate=2015-05-29|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203151029/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/disney-indias-pk-get-broad-759208|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 市场营销 ===
2014年7月31日，先行版海报发布。同日动态海报于[[YouTube|YouTube]]发布。第二张海报于2014年8月20日在[[孟买|孟买]]的活动上发布。阿米尔·汗在这张新海报中穿着拉贾斯坦邦传统服饰，戴着一副深色运动墨镜，手里拿着一个圆号。按照电影的宣传策略，制片方于第二张海报公布时透露<ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan covers up for second 'PK' poster|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/aamir-khan-covers-up-for-second-pk-poster|work=The Indian Express|date=2014-08-21|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214111821/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/aamir-khan-covers-up-for-second-pk-poster/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan unveils second 'PK' poster, beats retreat on nudity backlash|url=http://www.financialexpress.com/news/aamir-khan-unveils-second-pk-poster-beats-retreat-on-nudity-backlash/1281025|work=The Financial Express (India)|date=2014-08-21|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2014-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017044245/http://www.financialexpress.com/news/aamir-khan-unveils-second-pk-poster-beats-retreat-on-nudity-backlash/1281025|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第三张动态海报介绍了饰演拜龙·辛格的桑贾·伊杜特。第四张动态海报出现了饰演贾古·贾娜妮的艾鲁丝卡·沙玛和阿米尔·汗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.ibnlive.com/news/pk-finally-anushka-sharma-features-in-the-fourth-poster-of-the-film-along-with-aamir-khan/506722-8-66.html|title=PK: Finally, Anushka Sharma features in the fourth poster of the film along with Aamir Khan|date=2014-10-17|publisher=CNN-IBN|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027163231/http://m.ibnlive.com/news/pk-finally-anushka-sharma-features-in-the-fourth-poster-of-the-film-along-with-aamir-khan/506722-8-66.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿米尔·汗表示，影片的海报宣传战略是每辆到三周发布一张新海报。截至上映当日，已有8到10张海报发布<ref>{{cite web|title=PK will be promoted with a series of posters|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/pk-will-be-promoted-with-a-series-of-posters|work=The Indian Express|date=2014-08-29|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206172652/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/pk-will-be-promoted-with-a-series-of-posters/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Want to confuse the audience with every poster of PK'- Aamir Khan|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-want-to-confuse-the-audience-with-every-poster-of-pk-aamir-khan-2012417|publisher=Daily News and Analysis|date=2014-08-21|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205032831/https://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-want-to-confuse-the-audience-with-every-poster-of-pk-aamir-khan-2012417|dead-url=no}}</ref>。预告片于10月23日发布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82ZEDGPCkT8|title=PK Official Teaser I Releasing December 19, 2014|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121000554/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=82ZEDGPCkT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片的首张海报引发了争议，因为阿米尔·汗几乎全身赤裸地登场，只用收音机遮住生殖器<ref name="bare">{{cite web|title=FIRST LOOK: Aamir Khan bares all for PK!|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/first-look-aamir-khan-bares-all-for-pk/20140801.htm|publisher=Rediff.com|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203071958/https://www.rediff.com/movies/report/first-look-aamir-khan-bares-all-for-pk/20140801.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=PK poster: Here are 5 questions we have for the very naked Aamir Khan|url=http://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/pk-poster-here-are-5-questions-we-have-for-the-very-naked-aamir-khan-1644549.html|work=First Post|website=|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914120519/https://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/pk-poster-here-are-5-questions-we-have-for-the-very-naked-aamir-khan-1644549.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管[[电影认证中央委员会|电影认证中央委员会]]已经批准电影上映，但印度人权组织和社会正义阵线向法庭申请公共利益诉讼，认为电影裸体和粗俗，要求禁止其上映。最高法院驳回了上诉，还给电影开了绿灯<ref>{{cite web|title=Supreme Court snubs nude poster, gives green signal to Aamir Khan's PK|url=http://news.oneindia.in/india/aamir-khan-nude-poster-supreme-court-gives-green-signal-to-pk-bollywood-movie-1502475.html|publisher=Oneindia.in|date=2014-08-14|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2014-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019055622/http://news.oneindia.in/india/aamir-khan-nude-poster-supreme-court-gives-green-signal-to-pk-bollywood-movie-1502475.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/indiahome/indianews/article-2725459/Let-art-remain-art-SC-judge-refuses-ban-film-based-vulgar-nudity.html|title='Let art remain art': SC judge refuses to ban film based on 'vulgar' nudity|work=Daily Mail|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045849/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/indiahome/indianews/article-2725459/Let-art-remain-art-SC-judge-refuses-ban-film-based-vulgar-nudity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拉贾斯坦邦提交了一个针对阿米尔·汗和拉库马·希拉尼的诉讼<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/case-lodged-against-pk-actor-aamir-khan-director-raju-hirani-and-producer-in-rajasthan/|title=Case lodged against 'PK' actor Aamir Khan, director Raju Hirani and producer in Rajasthan|work=The Indian Express|date=2015-01-17|accessdate=2015-06-13|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030145925/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/case-lodged-against-pk-actor-aamir-khan-director-raju-hirani-and-producer-in-rajasthan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

