vandalized-by-Bajrang-Dal-members/articleshow/45675197.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时发动反对电影的公共利益诉讼<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Saffron-wings-protest-against-anti-Hindu-scenes-in-film-PK/articleshow/45680709.cms|title = Saffron wings protest against "anti-Hindu" scenes in film PK|last = Gupta|first = Suchandana|work = The Times of India|date = 2014-12-29|accessdate = 2015-06-14|archive-date = 2020-11-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111220207/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Saffron-wings-protest-against-anti-Hindu-scenes-in-film-PK/articleshow/45680709.cms|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/pil-seeks-ban-on-pk/article6716706.ece|title=PIL seeks ban on PK|author=Sandeep Joshi|work=The Hindu|accessdate=2015-06-14|archive-date=2019-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191203161832/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/pil-seeks-ban-on-pk/article6716706.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[北方邦|北方邦]]首长雅达夫·阿克什勒什和[[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]首长吉坦拉穆·曼杰辛等政府官员则免征电影的娱乐税，鼓励更多民众观看电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/aamir-khans-pk-tax-free-in-uttar-pradesh/articleshow/45703167.cms|title=Aamir Khan's 'PK' tax-free in Uttar Pradesh|work=The Economic Times|date=2014-12-31|accessdate=2015-06-14|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101032723/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/aamir-khans-pk-tax-free-in-uttar-pradesh/articleshow/45703167.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

