in>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2015/05/25/box-office-aamir-khan-bollywood-blockbuster-pk-sizzles-into-chinas-record-books/|title=Box Office: Aamir Khan Bollywood Blockbuster "PK" Sizzles Into China's Record Books|author=Rob Cain|work=Forbes|publisher=(Forbes, Inc.)|date=2015-05-25|accessdate=2015-05-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094559/https://www.forbes.com/sites/robcain/2015/05/25/box-office-aamir-khan-bollywood-blockbuster-pk-sizzles-into-chinas-record-books/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，截至2015年6月14日，票房已达到1880万美元<ref name=variety>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/china-box-office-jurassic-world-chomps-99-million-opening-weekend-1201520449/|title=China Box Office: ‘Jurassic World’ Chomps $99 Million Opening Weekend|author=Patrick Frater|work=variety.com|date=2015-06-14|accessdate=2015-06-16|archive-date=2019-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204200137/https://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/china-box-office-jurassic-world-chomps-99-million-opening-weekend-1201520449/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片成为首部突破1亿人民币门槛的印度电影，成为了为数不多的打破这道门槛的非好莱坞外语片<ref name="CHINA">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-box-office-san-andreas-801168|title=China Box Office: 'San Andreas' Shakes Up World's Second Biggest Film Market|author=Clifford Coonan|work=The Hollywood Reporter|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2015-06-08|accessdate=2015-06-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108154945/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-box-office-san-andreas-801168|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终成绩为1.18亿人民币<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.1905.com/news/20150623/904057.shtml#p1 |title=内地票房：《侏罗纪世界》连庄 端午节档吸金6亿 |accessdate=2015-06-24 |archive-date=2019-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205082506/https://www.1905.com/news/20150623/904057.shtml#p1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

